{"tid":1096670,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"因龍客機高雄赴港 起飛後傳爆炸聲折返","createTime":"2019-04-08T01:05:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-08T01:16:58.000Z","uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"946983813bc316ab6ff6ca4ec3a4886a8343b32e","tid":1096670,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T01:05:53.000Z","msg":"港龍航空公司一架從高雄飛往香港的客機，今早（8日）8時許起飛後不久即折返。台媒報道指，客機在空中曾傳出多下爆炸聲，有當地居民更稱看到飛機機翼起火，甚至放油。客機在外海盤旋折返小港機場降落，機場方面有4個消防分隊在跑道待命，客機現已安全降落。報道亦指，客機疑遭鳥擊，當局正了解事件。"},{"pid":"74d5762e58ceee012116af34a4ecc514553f59dc","tid":1096670,"uid":17641,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T01:08:05.000Z","msg":"韓國瑜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1b58c01fe1e76310fa98a21683152b99700607d","tid":1096670,"uid":53466,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T01:08:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"59e29d386862dbf7b126688e3f8ba90ace5dea07","tid":1096670,"uid":12021,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T01:08:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a5ea934ea72be8d32f846ec8069c28ed732e2715","tid":1096670,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e1b58c01fe1e76310fa98a21683152b99700607d","tid":1096670,"uid":53466,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T01:08:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T01:09:31.000Z","msg":"?"},{"pid":"b33aa22674d9a9906ebb8ef9b45a0ba36dec32a1","tid":1096670,"uid":21028,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T01:15:02.000Z","msg":"放油好正常"},{"pid":"b4fbac87518ce87ea09417851753e939f6ecb18a","tid":1096670,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T01:16:58.000Z","msg":"恐襲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}